How sketchy are you?

i randomly saw some pictures this girl took at like a bithday party or whatever and she was having such a good time and she was surrounded by all of her friends,and they were just being...themselves? and i think im really missing that as of late. i know i probably sound so redundant but so what. When people come home from college things feel "normal" again..to me atleast...and thats a really great feeling to me because i guess thats just what im used to?
I was thinking about the early days of high school(again) when all of us said we dont care about what people say, and when i thought i knew who i was,and when a huge sleepover was the highlight of my weekend... i remember when me julia and nina were really close, we would alternate houses every weekend haha.  Sharing rides to movies...my mom would never want to take us but i always asked her anyways...
then people change. for the better? i dunno.....maybe i changed and everyone else stayed the same. for the better? i dunno.
cuz now...now its about the drinking and the sex and for some people the drugs..and i do care what people think and i dont know who i am..now i drive to movies, and we "dont do" sleepovers..only when its to crash after drinking cuz i cant go home.

im just feeling like i fucked up (as usual) and i let my parents down...in turn let myself down.
Im stubborn, thats what my problem is..i thought i had everything under control...what an idiot i am...ill live it down though....i have to prove something to myself

____________________________________________________________________________________

on a brighter note i found out Karrie gets paid more than me and if i remember correctly i think she just started like 3 weeks ago?!
What the fuck do i have something on my ass that says "will work for less" ?
For serious now.
but there have been some pretty funny people that come in..

OldLady: is that soft cheese?
me:ummm its fresh? if thats what you mean?
OldLady:no! is it SOFT cheese.
me: no, but i can heat it up for you?
OldLady: *walks out of the store*
...later i realized what the hell she meant she wanted like speadable cheese like brie or some shit....
NEWSFLASH: ITS SUBWAYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY!!!!!!!!!

Pittsfordlady: mmmmmk im gonna need 2 subs
me: aright, what kinda of breads are they on?

me: Oh, im sorry we dont have any wheat right now its still baking
pittsfordlady:..oh...well how long till its done?
me: about 30 mins
pittsfordlady: *walks out of store*

HAHAHAHAHHA some people i just dont understand... just get a different kind of bread dont let it ruin ur day?

that whole wheat and "soft cheese" really does get to people
